snippet.title: 1 minute platinum | The Jumping Nuggets: Turbo
snippet.description:
The Jumping Nuggets comes again, but with Turbo version. The only difference between Turbo and "normal" version is that in Turbo, nuggets jumps much faster and after jumping 500 times there's a bit of wait until trophies finish popping out. But for those who loves hearing those bling bling sounds of trophies popping out, it's a bliss. 

Big thanks to Thilo Kruczek from ThiGames for providing me once again with the code for this game, your continuous support is amazing! 
Music from the game is enabled in this video with express permission from the developer and publisher. 

If you like The Jumping games, please support @ThiGames on YouTube as well.
